quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  4,114,"Aîas n wayen qqaôen ur imâin, siwa ayen iumôen ssadaqa, ne$ lqanun, ne$ lemûalêa ger medden. Win ixedmen aya, issarem ad Iôavi Öebbi, deqqal ad as Nefk arraz ameqwôaêan"
  4,115,"Win ixuûmen Amazan, mbaâd ma tepwabeggen as d nnhaya, iteddun d ubrid ur d wid n lmumnin, a t Neoo akken iooa. A t Nenheô ar Loahennama. A tu$alin tucmip"
  4,116,"Ih, Öebbi ur Ipsemmiê ma ad aS carken. Ipsemmiê ayen nniven, i win i S ihwan. Win icurken i Öebbi, innetlef ttelfan u$miq"
  4,117,"La pnujun ar nnta, war Neppa. La pnujun kan ar Cciîan aballa"
  4,118,"Ixza t Öebbi. Inna: \"ad awi$ amur ippuêeppmen, seg imdanen ik"
  4,119,"A ten telfe$, a ten ssenêesse$, ad asen amôe$ ad gezmen imeééu$en ubeqôi, ad asen amôe$ ad bedlen lxelq n Öebbi\". Win idmen Cciîan d bab, war Öebbi, ixseô lexsaôa n tidep"
  4,120,"Ipâahad asen, issenêas iten. Ayen i sen iâahed Cciîan, d a$uôôu kan"
  4,121,"Widak, axxam nnsen d Loahennama, ur ppafen, segs, tisensert"
  4,122,"Wid iumnen, u xeddmen ayen ilhan, a ten Nessekcem ar leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, degsen ad wekkôen, i lebda. Lemâahda n Öebbi a ppevôu. Anwa issawalen tidep sennig Öebbi"
  4,123,"Ur illi s usirem nnwen, ne$ s win n At Tezmamt. Win ixedmen cceôô, ad ippuqeîîi fellas. Ur Ippaf, war Öebbi, bab ne$ asettaô"
  4,124,"Win ixeddmen ayen ilhan, d ddkeô ne$ d nnta, u neppa iumen…, widak ad kecmen Loennet, ur pwadensen s yiclem utemôiw"
  4,125,"Anwa iûegmen ddin is sennig win iunzen i Öebbi, u neppa d laâûem, u idda d ddin n Ibôahim, i imalen ar tidep? Öebbi Irra Ibôahim d aêbib"
  4,126,"N Öebbi i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Öebbi Izga Izzi i yal cci"
  4,127,"Steqsayen k $ef tlawin. Ini: \"Öebbi ad awen Issefhem fellasent. Ayen i wen $ôan di Tezmamt, $ef tlawin tigujilin, iwumi ur tefkim ara i sent iuran, u teb$am a tent ta$em. Akked igwerdan imeéyanen. A pbeddem i igujilen s lmizan. Ayen akw txeddmem n lxiô, Öebbi, s tidep, Izga Iéôa t"
  4,128,"Ma tugad tmeîîut ad as ibru, ne$ ad as iwexxeô urgaz is, ulac u$ilif fellasen ma ufan lemwafaqa garasen. Ppif lemwafaqa. Imdanen, deg iman nnsen d imceôôiyen. Ma tgerzem u têezzbem, Öebbi, s tidep, Izga Iéôa ayen txeddmem"
  4,129,"Ur tezmirem a ppeddum s lmizan, ger tlawin, xas teb$am. Ihi, ur pmalet yal tumlin a p teooem, amzun d tamejgugelt. Ma tgam ayen ilhan, u têezzbem, s tidep, Öebbi Izga Ipsemmiê, Ipêunu"
  4,130,"Ma mfaôaqen, ad I$it Öebbi yal wa, s ôôeéq iS. Öebbi Izga d Ajemmal, d Bab n ûûwab"
  4,131,"N Öebbi i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Ni$ Nweûûa wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, uqbel nnwen, u Nweûûa kwen, a pêezzbem i Öebbi. Ma tnekôem, ihi, n Öebbi i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Öebbi Izga d Asâay, d Amaâzuz"
  4,132,"N Öebbi i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Nesteqnaâ s Öebbi d Awkil"
  4,133,"Ma ihwa yaS, a kwen Ikkes a yimdanen! A d Iawi wiyav. Öebbi Izga Izmer i waya"
  4,134,"Win ib$an a$ellet n ddunit, ihi, ar Öebbi a$ellet n ddunit akked win n laxeôt. Öebbi Izga Issel, Ipwali"